            "heading": "WHAT’S INCLUDED",
            "content": "<p>Arccos Air wearable — lightweight and weather resistant. Less than 25 grams.</p><p>Wireless charging case — keeps your wearable charged for up to 12 rounds.</p><p>Requires an active Game Tracking subscription.</p>",
