        "collapsible_tab_8k8GAY": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DO I NEED SENSORS ON MY CLUBS?",
            "content": "<p>No. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, you can add Smart Sensors at any time — but they're completely optional.<br/><br/>Compatible with iOS. Android sensorless compatibility coming soon.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_MpB3Wt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DO I NEED TO CARRY MY PHONE?",
            "content": "<p>No! That's one of the biggest differences with Arccos Air. The wearable replaces the need for your phone or an Apple Watch on the course. Slip the AI wearable in your pocket, or clip it on your belt, and play. Your shot data syncs to the app after your round or whenever you're back in range.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_mx4AbJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DOES THIS WORK WITH ANDROID?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Arccos Air works with Android for phone-free play, but currently requires Smart Sensors. Sensorless functionality is coming to Android soon.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_CrEQGE": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
